== 现代使用 ==
五大是五個對北美音樂歷史有重大影響的管弦樂團之美譽，當今美國最高水準的管弦樂團為數眾多，持續使用五大而將其他管弦樂團劃入下一個等級的這種區分法可能會過時，但是仍然是標誌著北美樂團的素質。许多管弦乐团都曾被音乐评论家提及，认为其水平高超可以加入五大管弦乐团的名单与之并列。这些乐团包括[[洛杉矶爱乐乐团|洛杉矶爱乐乐团]]<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=美国“五大交响乐团”是伪概念？|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/culture/20130625/c25five/|access-date=2022-03-10|date=2013-06-25|last=Oestreich|first=James R.|work=纽约时报中文网|language=zh-cn}}</ref><ref name="Swed05">{{Cite web|title=Time to get on the stick|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2005/aug/14/entertainment/ca-orchestras14|access-date=2010-07-18|author=Mark Swed|date=2005-08-14|publisher=''Los Angeles Times''|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025100825/http://articles.latimes.com/2005/aug/14/entertainment/ca-orchestras14|archive-date=2012-10-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[旧金山交响乐团|旧金山交响乐团]]<ref name=":1" /><ref name="Swed05" />、[[亚特兰大交响乐团|亚特兰大交响乐团]]<ref>Glynn, Mary Ann, [http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=SlJPJWzv-qkC&pg=PA65&dq=%22big+five%22+orchestras&hl=en&ei=PtdCTNaCL5-IOOeFnZ0N&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=8&ved=0CE4Q6AEwBzgU#v=onepage&q=%22big%20five%22%20orchestras&f=false "Maestro or Manager?] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=SlJPJWzv-qkC&pg=PA65&dq=%22big+five%22+orchestras&hl=en&ei=PtdCTNaCL5-IOOeFnZ0N&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=8&ved=0CE4Q6AEwBzgU#v=onepage&q=%22big%20five%22%20orchestras&f=false|date=20140911172518}} in Joseph Lampel, Jamal Shamsie, Theresa K. Lant (eds.), ''The business of culture'', Routledge, 2006, p. 65. ISBN 0805855823</ref>、[[匹兹堡交响乐团|匹兹堡交响乐团]]<ref name="Time 2">{{Cite web|title=Orchestras: The Elite Eleven|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,835298,00.html|access-date=2010-04-16|date=1966-04-08|publisher=''Time''|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119140728/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,835298,00.html|archive-date=2012-01-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[休斯顿交响乐团|休斯顿交响乐团]]<ref name="Time 2" />、[[巴尔的摩交响乐团|巴尔的摩交响乐团]]<ref name=":0">Kosman, Joshua, [http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=m-2GjJ0BjpMC&pg=PA24&dq=%22big+five%22+orchestras&hl=en&ei=dNRCTKSmDIaVOLzFxeMM&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CDUQ6AEwAjgU#v=onepage&q=%22big%20five%22%20orchestras&f=false "New Music for a New Century"] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=m-2GjJ0BjpMC&pg=PA24&dq=%22big+five%22+orchestras&hl=en&ei=dNRCTKSmDIaVOLzFxeMM&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CDUQ6AEwAjgU#v=onepage&q=%22big%20five%22%20orchestras&f=false|date=20140911150235}}, ''The Arts Today'', USIA, Vol. 3., No. 1, June 2008, p. 25. ISBN 1428967346</ref>、[[國家交響樂團_(美國)|国家交响乐团]]<ref name=":0" />、[[明尼苏达管弦乐团|明尼苏达管弦乐团]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Orchestras: Big Five Plus One?|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,837547,00.html|access-date=2010-07-18|date=1967-11-10|publisher=''Time''|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111223000445/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,837547,00.html|archive-date=2011-12-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>以及[[圣路易斯交响乐团|圣路易斯交响乐团]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Big 5 orchestras: Do they still reign supreme?|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-8242788.html|access-date=2010-07-18|author=Dyer, Richard|date=1993-08-29|publisher=''The Boston Globe''|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106060055/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-8242788.html|archive-date=2012-11-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

